<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Reactivated - {{company}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; max-width: 400px; }
        .icon { font-size: 50px; color: #28a745; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h1 { color: #333; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { color: #666; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .login-btn { background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">✓</div>
        <h1>Successfully Reactivated!</h1>
        <p>Hello {{firstName}}, your account is now active. You can now log in using your existing password.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">If you have questions, contact our support team. <br> © {{year}} {{company}}</div>
</body>
</html>

